c%C3%BAc/poem-CoQmASZ2XBgjYRkCn3_SnA">Phỏng cúc - 訪菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C4%A9nh-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-mai/poem-ydVZshZwGmCjvIpEF2qCMw">Tặng Lĩnh Thượng mai - 贈嶺上梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/T%C3%A2y-chinh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-t%C3%A1i-chinh-Ai-Lao/poem-RXZSBGhcbxmUwAdHAZK0pg">Tây chinh đạo trung (tái chinh Ai Lao) - 西征道中（再征哀牢）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-IV/poem-Pr5bZbe6uKNY9RWwhLqSnA">Vô đề (IV) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/author-1swHDuDfqhjQRVvirtpDBQ">Phạm Kỳ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
